Recommended packages

sudo pacman -S --needed \
    ttf-dejavu \
    ttf-liberation \
    noto-fonts \
    noto-fonts-cjk \
    noto-fonts-emoji \
    ttf-font-awesome \
    ttf-iosevka-nerd \
    ttf-inconsolata-nerd \
    ttf-ibmplex-mono-nerd

(installs basically any font you will ever need)
also, this whole install is ~700 megabytes AT MOST so dont worry about that.
again, this will cover basically any font/emoticon you will ever need, unless you visit something extremely neiche like Egyptian hieroglyphs
